{"success": true, "message": "Fetched question.", "data": {"showTimer": true, "showAttemptInsight": true, "playSounds": true, "dontShowCorrectAnswerImmediately": false, "_id": "6151e863515a310b39a4a5cf", "type": "singleCorrect", "level": null, "category": null, "approximateTimeRequired": null, "imageBaseUrl": null, "helperText": null, "source": "NTAS1", "classes": [], "exams": ["615d76b2c52ffa3c944600df"], "subjects": ["615d708dbd4a37c4058ee5a8"], "chapters": ["615d6fec2b295b085ab6eb8e"], "topics": [], "concepts": [], "microConcepts": [], "questionLabels": [{"title": "NTA Abhyas Paper", "value": "73", "isVisible": true}], "previousYearPapers": [], "question": {"text": "A small bead of mass <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>m</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mi>kg</mi></math>&nbsp;is free to move on a circular hoop. The circular hoop has centre at&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">C</mi></math> and radius<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mi>r</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">m</mi></math> and it rotates about a fixed vertical axis. The coefficient of friction between bead and hoop is <math><mi>\u03bc</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0.5</mn></math> . The maximum angular speed of the hoop for which the bead does not have relative motion with respect to the hoop, at the position shown in the figure is: (Take <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>g</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>10</mn><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">&nbsp;</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">m</mi><mo>&nbsp;</mo><msup><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">s</mi><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup></math> )<br />\r<br />\r<img alt=\"\" height=\"234\" src=\"https://cdn-question-pool.getmarks.app/nta_abhyas/jee_main/images/ci/image2-b93ca5d7-37ee-4317-996b-e9715da5fea1.jpg\" style=\"max-width:\"100%\"; object-fit:contain\" width=\"139\" />", "image": null}, "options": [{"id": "5uwjx", "text": "<math><msup><mrow><mfenced separators=\"|\"><mrow><mn>5</mn><msqrt><mn>2</mn></msqrt></mrow></mfenced></mrow><mrow><mfrac><mrow><mn>1</mn></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn></mrow></mfrac></mrow></msup></math>", "image": null, "isCorrect": false}, {"id": "dtkc2", "text": "<math><msup><mrow><mfenced separators=\"|\"><mrow><mn>10</mn><msqrt><mn>2</mn></msqrt></mrow></mfenced></mrow><mrow><mfrac><mrow><mn>1</mn></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn></mrow></mfrac></mrow></msup></math>", "image": null, "isCorrect": false}, {"id": "QDEQu", "text": "<math><msup><mrow><mfenced separators=\"|\"><mrow><mn>15</mn><msqrt><mn>2</mn></msqrt></mrow></mfenced></mrow><mrow><mfrac><mrow><mn>1</mn></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn></mrow></mfrac></mrow></msup></math>", "image": null, "isCorrect": false}, {"id": "3Lu9z", "text": "<math><msup><mrow><mfenced separators=\"|\"><mrow><mn>30</mn><msqrt><mn>2</mn></msqrt></mrow></mfenced></mrow><mrow><mfrac><mrow><mn>1</mn></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn></mrow></mfrac></mrow></msup></math>", "image": null, "isCorrect": true}], "correctValue": null, "solution": {"text": "The maximum angular speed of the hoop corresponds to the situation when the bead is just about to slide upwards.<br />The free-body diagram of the bead is<br /><br /><img alt=\"\" height=\"166\" src=\"https://cdn-question-pool.getmarks.app/nta_abhyas/jee_main/images/ci/image3-b1c22648-d561-4333-95d8-db75257ec90a.jpg\" style=\"max-width:\"100%\"; object-fit:contain\" width=\"394\" /><br /><br />For the bead not to slide upwards<br /><br /><math><mi>m</mi><msup><mrow><mi>&#969;</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup><mo>(</mo><mi>r</mi><mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">sin</mi></mrow><mo>&#8289;</mo><mrow><msup><mrow><mn>45</mn></mrow><mrow><mi>o</mi></mrow></msup><mo>)</mo><mi>&#160;</mi><mi>c</mi><mi>o</mi><mi>s</mi></mrow></mrow><mi>&#160;</mi><msup><mrow><mn>45</mn></mrow><mrow><mi>o</mi></mrow></msup><mo>-</mo><mi>m</mi><mi>g</mi><mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">sin</mi></mrow><mo>&#8289;</mo><mrow><msup><mrow><mn>45</mn></mrow><mrow><mi>o</mi></mrow></msup></mrow></mrow><mo>&#60;</mo><mi>&#956;</mi><mi>N</mi></math> ...(i)<br /><br />Where <math><mi>N</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>m</mi><mi>g</mi><mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">cos</mi></mrow><mo>&#8289;</mo><mrow><msup><mrow><mn>45</mn></mrow><mrow><mi>o</mi></mrow></msup></mrow></mrow><mo>+</mo><mi>m</mi><msup><mrow><mi>&#969;</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup><mo>(</mo><mi>r</mi><mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">sin</mi></mrow><mo>&#8289;</mo><mrow><msup><mrow><mn>45</mn></mrow><mrow><mi>o</mi></mrow></msup><mo>)</mo><mi>&#160;</mi></mrow></mrow><mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">sin</mi></mrow><mo>&#8289;</mo><mrow><msup><mrow><mn>45</mn></mrow><mrow><mi>o</mi></mrow></msup></mrow></mrow></math> ...(ii)<br /><br />From (i) and (ii) we get,<br /><br /><math><mi>&#969;</mi><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mn>30</mn><msqrt><mn>2</mn></msqrt></msqrt></math>&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>rad</mi><mo>&#160;</mo><msup><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">s</mi><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></math>", "image": null}, "videoSolution": null, "numericalLowerLimit": null, "numericalUpperLimit": null, "cpyqbSubjects": ["61bb58181213731910ea0b70", "61c055eae8ce0dc8a5c62d33", "616057750283de43c87e3e1b", "61964fe0a5a5260118868021", "61964f81a5a526011886801d", "629f39e4ac11b26562e0625b", "616057920283de43c87e3e1e", "615f0c729476412f48314dab", "61a8a2c2e8ce0dc8a5c62d2d", "629105adee9e3ae00d63352b", "629f385f263330a77be9fa7d", "616056cd0283de43c87e3e15", "616057190283de43c87e3e18", "62962075e7f8e9ac4daeafd7", "64d50bd73df7f4a7f3017f6f", "66b79b34d4b564dfab4f94cc", "678ea9a09cc79e5f592bdc11", "67fa5fef4468eb1307ceb0ad", "6807d2ad647479b8e8696479"], "cpyqbChapters": ["616023b74026d68c120f2ba9", "616023b9c2e3bbfc3f2ecdd2", "616023b78dba43da23bef37e", "616023b542cfec4323be20b3", "61964c74ec1ca6c1a7365dcf", "61bb821fa52006d37a60e707", "61c089a30f62a0d239520145", "61964c76bae973f89e899882", "61e7bd7991a3d6916